---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Return Policy | Purest Electrolyte" description="Our 30-day satisfaction guarantee — we stand behind every jar.">
  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Return Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-10">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Our 30-Day Satisfaction Guarantee</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        We stand behind every jar of Purest Electrolyte — and we mean that. If you're not happy with your purchase for any reason, contact us within 30 days of delivery and we'll make it right. No hassle. No hard feelings.
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-600">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span> Don't love the flavor? We'll swap it for a different one.</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span> Not satisfied? We'll refund your order.</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span> No return shipping required.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Damaged or Wrong Item</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        If your order arrives damaged or you received the wrong item, we'll send a replacement immediately — no questions asked. Just send us a quick note and a photo if possible.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">How to Reach Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@purestelectrolytes.com" class="text-green-700 underline">hello@purestelectrolytes.com</a> with your order number and we'll take care of you right away.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">A Note on Third-Party Retailers</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Our satisfaction guarantee applies to orders placed directly through purestelectrolytes.com. For purchases made through third-party retailers, please contact the retailer directly.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8">
      <p class="text-green-800 font-medium text-center">
        Questions? We're real people who actually care. Reach out anytime — we'll make it right. 🥥
      </p>
    </div>

  </main>
</Layout>
